You know, honey, your
mother is very worried.

76
00:04:23,931 --> 00:04:26,149
I don't want
to be transformed.

77
00:04:26,184 --> 00:04:27,650
I want to stay ugly.

78
00:04:27,685 --> 00:04:29,902
Oh, you're not ugly,
you're just...

79
00:04:29,937 --> 00:04:31,154
not beautiful.

80
