and he read books.

98
00:05:19,987 --> 00:05:22,205
We talked a lot,
just the two of us.

99
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,206
Everybody talks.

100
00:05:23,241 --> 00:05:24,707
I mean about
real things

101
00:05:24,742 --> 00:05:27,710
not just about
electronic baseball
or super soccer

102
00:05:27,745 --> 00:05:29,462
and where to buy
your clothes

103
