Yes, she did.

128
00:06:25,553 --> 00:06:27,520
Don't you think you're
being awfully silly?

129
00:06:27,555 --> 00:06:30,022
No. There's no law, is there?

130
00:06:30,057 --> 00:06:32,275
But it isn't as if
it hurts or anything.

131
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:35,027
