a new hairstyle

138
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,175
or new clothes or something.

139
00:06:49,425 --> 00:06:50,927
You just look better.

140
00:06:50,962 --> 00:06:52,929
I'll look like
one of those drawings

141
